settings.title: founders
settings.content:
Better Bet was founded in 2020 by Aman, Sweta and Pavitra who are all passionate vegans. The idea for the company was born out of their struggles to find a great-tasting milk alternative that could be used in a variety of ways.

Our team is made up of passionate individuals who share a commitment to promoting a healthy and sustainable lifestyle. We are driven by a desire to make a positive impact on the world and are dedicated to creating high-quality, delicious plant-based milk alternatives. Our team consists of experts in various fields, including food science, nutrition, and sustainability, and we work together to achieve our mission.

settings.title: Superheros
settings.html: After conducting extensive research and development, they created the world's first plant-based milk made of sprouted millets and grains. Better Bet has since become a leader in the plant-based milk industry and continues to innovate and improve its products

settings.title: CREATE A POSITIVE IMPACT
settings.html: At Better Bet, we believe in giving back to the community and protecting the environment. We are committed to using sustainable ingredients and manufacturing processes, reducing waste, and supporting local farmers. We also donate to organizations that promote animal welfare and environmental sustainability. We strive to be a responsible and ethical company that makes a positive impact on the world.
